title: 12 Peach Tree Ln.
posting_body: ['Beautiful two story townhouse in the Orchard Gate Community in Westmont.', 'Large floor plan with vaulted ceilings in master bedroom and roman tub with jacuzzi in master bathroom.', 'The property is recently remodeled with a new hardwood flooring throughout and a paint job.', 'It also contains sliding glass doors to patio, 1st floor laundry and one car attached garage.', 'Great location, close to schools, shopping and transportation.', 'The wonderful townhouse, its location, schools and the complex overall make it one of the most sought after and desirable places to live in.', 'Essential Information,', 'Price: $1700, Bedrooms: 2, Bathrooms: 2.5, Sq.', 'Ft.: 1,400 sq.', 'ft.', 'Address: 12 Peach Tree Ln.', 'Westmont Illinois 60559', 'Available: September 01, 2022', 'Amenities,', 'Common Insurance, Lawn Care, Snow Removal.', 'Exterior Maintenance.', 'School Information,', 'Elementary - Maercker Elementary School', 'Middle - Westview Hills Middle School', 'High -- Downers Grove South High School', 'For more information, please contact:', 'Joe Thaqi', '708-642-3215']
